data.name: lblIntro1.Text
data.value:
Ten years have passed since the Zin'Xi decimated the planet Earth. Now, after years surving the barren wastes of your home, you must take revenge, retaking the once-colonies of Earth.
During your mission, you will visit the seven planets that were once earth colonies:
Alpha Centuri, Pollux, Formalhaut, Kepler, Tres, Cetus, and Pyxis
The year is 2158
